  • Constructor Details

    • User

      public User()
      Default constructor. Initializes empty HashMaps for waiting lists, event history, and created events.

    • User

      public User(String userId, String name, String email, String phone, String role, boolean notificationsEnabled, String deviceId, long createdAt)
      Constructs a new User with specified details. Also initializes empty maps for event-related data.
      Parameters:
      userId - The unique identifier for the user.
      name - The user's full name.
      email - The user's email address.
      phone - The user's phone number.
      role - The user's role (e.g., "entrant", "organizer").
      notificationsEnabled - True if notifications are enabled, false otherwise.
      deviceId - The unique ID of the user's device (for notifications).
      createdAt - The timestamp (long) when the user account was created.
